      "content": "it's not just \"noise\" though. it's constant. i cant even go to class or sleep without thinking about the next thing they're gonna post about me. it feels like the whole world is just watching me fail and enjoying it. i feel like i'm stuck in this loop and there's no way to fix it. like, how am i supposed to have a future when this is all anyone sees?",
