      "content": "i've tried talking to people but nothing changes. they just say \"it'll get better\" or \"just ignore them\" but they don't get it. it's not gonna get better. the more i try to fix it, the worse it gets. i just want the feeling to stop. i just want to be able to rest and not have to deal with any of this anymore. it feels like the only way to actually be safe is to just... not be here.",
