      "content": "I hear how much pain you're in, and it's completely understandable that you want the constant pressure to stop. When words like \"just ignore them\" feel so empty, it can make it seem like there is no way out of this nightmare. Please, please consider reaching out to a crisis counselor or a trusted adult who can listen without judgment and help you find real safety. You are not alone, and there are people ready to support you through this darkness.",
